@startuml
' 优化样式
skinparam dpi 150
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam nodesep 80

package "com.myapp.DuckComponent" {

    class DuckComponent <<JComponent>> {
        - name : String
        - isDonald : boolean
        - clothing : List<String>
        - currentStyle : String
        __
        + DuckComponent(name, isDonald)
        + addClothing(item : String)
        + removeClothing(item : String)
        .. 核心绘制入口 ..
        # paintComponent(g : Graphics)
        .. 基础层绘制 ..
        - drawDonaldDuck(...)
        - drawBabyDuck(...)
        - drawCasualBody(...)
        - drawFormalBody(...)
        .. 装饰层绘制 (Private Helpers) ..
        - drawAccessories(...)
        - drawHat(...)
        - drawGlasses(...)
        - drawTShirt(...)
        - drawOveralls(...)
        - drawSneakers(...)
        - ... (其他配饰方法)
    }
    
    note right of DuckComponent::paintComponent
      模板方法：
      1. 设置抗锯齿
      2. 绘制基础层 (Body)
      3. 绘制装饰层 (Accessories)
      4. 绘制标签
    end note

    note right of DuckComponent::addClothing
      包含业务逻辑：
      互斥检查 (如：
      添加背带裤时移除
      其他衣服)
    end note
}
@enduml